description:
The Real Housewives of New York are coming back in May! Danny recaps the trailer, plus this week's Real Housewives of New Jersey, which featured the cast heading down to the Jersey Shore. Over on Real Housewives of Dallas, the women argue over spirits and astroglide!


RHONJ Recap: 21:52ish

RHOD Recap: 37:01ish
